Plugin lets you embed Kommento Comments (https://kommento.webospace.com) in your Website or Blog

== Description ==

This plugin implements Kommento Comments Api for embedding Kommento Comments in your Website or Blog.

Kommento Single Sign On feature is supported.

The plugin embeds comments using Api Options as given in https://kommento.webospace.com/site/embed-comments

== Installation ==

This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.

1. Upload the plugin files to the `/wp-content/plugins/kommento` directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' screen in WordPress
3  Login/Register in https://kommento.webospace.com
4  Go to Dashboard and create Website
5  After creating website go to Kommento Credentials link in View Website Page.
6  Copy Kommento Id & Kommento Secret from Kommento Credentials Page
7  Go to WordPress Settings->Kommento screen to configure the plugin with the above details
8  Save the Settings and Kommento Comments will appear in place of WordPress Inbuild Comments

